VerbetesREST version 1
======================

	Verbetes project aims to develop an automatic approach to extract micro-biographies of entities (people, organizations, events, etc.) from text available on the web, mainly news articles, supported on well known open resources like Wikipedia and Freebase. 
	
	VerbetesREST is a RESTful interface for Verbetes data resources. Current version is publicly available online at SAPO services catalog (https://store.services.sapo.pt/en/Catalog/other/free-api-information-retrieval-verbetes). This version comprehends more than 100,000 names of public personalities mentioned on portuguese news articles and their jobs/positions. Successful online applications using Verbetes includes "Mundo Visto Daqui interativo" (http://voxx.sapo.pt/mvdi) and Voxx (http://voxx.sapo.pt).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DBI
  JSON
  XML::Simple
  Encode

